        Selling an Airbnb Property in Brisbane: What Short-Term Rental Owners Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        If your Brisbane property is listed on Airbnb or another short-term rental platform, selling it has a few extra moving parts. Here's what to work through before you go to market.
      </p>
